data.name: lblWiz.Text
data.value: Welcome to the WOL2 Network scanner. Please select a network interface in the list below. The scanner will automatically determine the subnet range. You may also manually specify the range in the format "[IP FROM] -[ IP TO] / [SUBNET MASK]". After scanning you can select the hosts you wish to add and press "Add".

data.name: label3.Text
data.value: Note: You can right click the hosts list to open a context menu.
